{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "INHTODKNGUBMFKU5TP4YKGZPQZDYJX4Q",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041129001",
    "title": "アーモンドアイ",
    "enTitle": "Almond Eye",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "とんでもない傑物が揃いました！　まさに夢の光景！",
            "enText": "We have an incredible lineup here! It's something straight out of a dream!",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 141,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": -8640408630197309123,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "時代を背負い、時代を作った名ウマ娘たちの戦いです！\nさあ、並び立つは――",
            "enText": "Each carrying the weight of an era on their shoulders, it's a \nshowdown between these famous Uma Musume! Now, lined up――",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 201,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": 1117029051570099173,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "みんなが愛するウマ娘、キタサンブラック！　『菊花賞』で\nGⅠ初勝利後、天皇賞春秋制覇と数々のレースで花火を打ち上げた！",
            "enText": "An Uma Musume beloved by all, Kitasan Black! After her \nfirst G1 victory at the 『Kikka Sho』, setting off fireworks \nin other races including the Spring and Autumn Tenno Sho!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 346,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 178,
                    "pathId": 434106151617625695
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 309,
                    "pathId": -4121649670954976271
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4116223223400970373,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "剛毅なる貴婦人、ジェンティルドンナ！　トリプルティアラを\n達成し、『ジャパンカップ』史上初の連覇と、歩む道は豪華絢爛！",
            "enText": "The Indomitable Noble Lady, Gentildonna! Obtaining the Triple \nTiara, and by becoming the first to claim consecutive victories \nat the 『Japan Cup』, forging her own awe-inspiring path!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 326,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2696340945593680518
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3607727782960365463
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -6550829455508886726
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -4035174706263733990
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8354890982704244014,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "時代を切り拓き、見る者の心を酔わせた名ウマ娘、ウオッカ！\n64年ぶりにティアラ路線から『日本ダービー』を制しました！",
            "enText": "Pioneering a new era, captivating everyone who saw her \nrun, Vodka! Breaking a 64 year drought by winning the \n『Japan Derby』 even as part of the Tiara rotation!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 329,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": 5536503407235378335
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": 3111552252026405710
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": 5718632621195274169
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": 6645289682634606942
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 641127820144809970,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "聞こえるか、彼女を称える旋律が！　テイエムオペラオー！\n8戦8勝の年間無敗という戦績から、世紀末覇王と呼ばれました！",
            "enText": "Can you hear the chorus of praise!? TM Opera O! With her undefeated \nrecord of 8 wins in 8 races, earning her the title Centurial Overlord!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 340,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": -7486393279953901495
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": 7441889445521695315
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 229,
                    "pathId": -5887287620876522227
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7228443090072430732,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "いずれも、芝GⅠ歴代最多7勝を挙げた凄まじいウマ娘たち！\nそして……そして！　最後は、やはり――！",
            "enText": "Each of them, incredible Uma Musume who have won 7 G1 turf races, \ntied for the most in history! And then……and then! Finally, it's――!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 310,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 368,
                    "pathId": -934790522091690443
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": 5909757578662487399
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6686876917404363906,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフ！！！",
            "enText": "Symboli Rudolf!!!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": -7179879256061667504
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": 7205464346639524518
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": 1644401104297658220
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 240,
                    "pathId": -7183108655454377907
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 164,
                    "pathId": 5046358526745856799
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 156,
                    "pathId": -2611900269305742947
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 159,
                    "pathId": 523819633560481992
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8867275531608613909,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "トゥインクル・シリーズ史上初の、無敗の三冠ウマ娘かつ、\nトゥインクル・シリーズ史上初の、芝GⅠ7勝達成ウマ娘！",
            "enText": "In the Twinkle Series, the first in history to become an \nundefeated Triple Crown Uma Musume! In the Twinkle Series, \nthe first Uma Musume in history to become a 7 time turf G1 Winner!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 322,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 398,
                    "pathId": -5834750910202677666
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 8433001838261992667
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 356,
                    "pathId": 3287150539581438961
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 412,
                    "pathId": -3949127337227314786
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -8451451332858795755
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1608991291522217504,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "実況",
            "enName": "Announcer",
            "jpText": "その『強い』勝ち方は、もはやレースの教科書！\n彼女の切り拓いた道こそが、まさに、レース界の王道であります！",
            "enText": "That 『Strength』 in victory, is already a part of Race History! \nThe path she's carved out is truly the Royal Road of the racing world!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 320,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 215,
                    "pathId": -3237869753981275230
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -5400524891788068896
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -1408810249347609242
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -5885317382710776115
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1935053173957063540,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "……有頂天外、と言うのかな。\nこんな機会をもらえるなんてね、逸る心が抑えきれない。",
            "enText": "……euphoria. I wonder if that's how to describe this. To be \ngiven such an opportunity, I can barely contain my excitement.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 314,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 582,
                    "pathId": 355808862516991946
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 236,
                    "pathId": -2490101404952374423
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 355,
                    "pathId": 7701029115301756589
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1000296037883693615,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "我々こそが、頂だ。かかってこい――",
            "enText": "Together, we stand at the summit. I stand ready――",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 162,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 4979069049885689671
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7652966431297401422
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 5366163530037906773
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8673821497840842739,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――ざわめきが聞こえる。\n向かう先……光の奥から、熱が、夢が、希望が零れてくる。",
            "enText": "――I could hear the commotion. Where I was heading……from the \ncenter of that light, passion, dreams, and aspirations overflowed.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 2088334467720251554
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7790583991718574812,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "誰もが待っているのだ。\n変化を。それを成すものを。",
            "enText": "Everyone was waiting. \nFor change. For the one to overturn it all.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -7747092290482560493
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6929795848648465956,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "それじゃあ、行ってくるわね……トレーナー。",
            "enText": "Then, I'm heading out……Trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 145,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ああ――アーモンドアイ。勝っておいで",
                    "enText": "Yeah――Almond Eye. Go out there and win",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "うん――アーモンドアイ。勝ってきて",
                    "enText": "Yeah――Almond Eye. Go out there and win",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 1393934024499072196
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2739712927780947652,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ええ。\nわたしが、勝つわ。すべてに。",
            "enText": "Right. \nI will win. Over everyone.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 176,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 209,
                    "pathId": 4663274843514081602
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3277868725866958462
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5027616640363988309,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "時代が変わる。\n――希望ではない。確信だった。",
            "enText": "The times will change. \n――This is not an aspiration. It is undeniable.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 130,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -8300220226643317415
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -26642348871350523,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう、始まりは――数年前のこと。",
            "enText": "And it all began――Several years ago.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 5557621006054322193,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――――ようやく。……ようやく、ようやく！",
            "enText": "――――Finally. ……Finally, finally!",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（ようやく、スタートに立てた！）",
                    "enText": "(I'm finally at the starting line!)",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5075171149976814850,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "中央トレーナーのライセンスを取得し、\nトレセン学園のトレーナーになれた！",
            "enText": "I obtained a trainer license for Central. \nI'm going to be a trainer at Tracen Academy!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 5534697577524388542,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "地に足つかず、ひとまず今後役立てられそうな本を探しに来ていた。\nレース教本、栄養学、解剖学――と、手元の山が積みあがっていく。",
            "enText": "To make sure I was firmly grounded, I came here looking \nfor some books that might be useful for me. Racing Textbooks, \nNutrition, Anatomy――the books were starting to pile up.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 127,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（可能な限りの準備をしておかなければ）",
                    "enText": "(I have to be as prepared as possible)",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（可能な限りの準備をしておかなくちゃ）",
                    "enText": "(I have to be as prepared as possible)",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4005163225162331463,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――時として、ウマ娘は\n『みんなの願いを乗せて走る存在』と言われることがある。",
            "enText": "――Sometimes, Uma Musume are called \n『Existences that carry the aspirations of everyone』",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 8509940328773043797,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "例えば、ドラマチックなまでの復活劇。例えば、効率化が\n重視される時代に逆らうような、不器用で破天荒なレース。",
            "enText": "Sometimes, a dramatic comeback. Or a graceless, \nunconventional race that throws everything out the window.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -3468747240700802595,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "願いは走りとなり、やがて誰かの心を救うことすらあるのだ。\nだからこそ――",
            "enText": "That a wish turns in to a run, one that \nmay even turn in to salvation. That's why――",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（俺は、妥協なくサポートしていきたい）",
                    "enText": "(I want to be the one to support them)",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（私は、妥協なくサポートしていきたい）",
                    "enText": "(I want to be the one to support them)",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5898670511241777722,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "これから出会う担当ウマ娘が、最大限の力を発揮して夢を叶え、\nそれが誰かの願いを叶えるほどの輝きとなれるように……！",
            "enText": "I hope the Uma Musume I'll be responsible for will be able to \nuse their full potential to make their dream come true. And to \nshine brightly enough that another will chase after them……!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 7223471183560448319,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "『――“GⅠ7勝超え”はどうすれば成せるのか……ですか。\n面白い質問ですね』",
            "enText": "[――How to become a \"7 G1 winner\"……is it? \nThat's quite an interesting question]",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 228,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "！",
                    "enText": "!",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -645296331944211313,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ふと顔をあげると……月刊トゥインクルが定期配信している\nトーク番組が、本屋のモニターで流れていた。",
            "enText": "I looked up……Monthly Twinkle, a recurring talk show \nbroadcast, was airing on one of the bookstore monitors.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 3671054132511918161,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "インタビュアー",
            "enName": "Interviewer",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフさんの到達したGⅠ7勝――\n並んだ方はいても、超えた方はいらっしゃいません。",
            "enText": "Symboli Rudolf-san, with 7 G1 wins――there are plenty who \nhave reached this milestone but none have surpassed it.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 249,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 329,
                    "pathId": 1272858058768161368
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2984144334774038216,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "インタビュアー",
            "enName": "Interviewer",
            "jpText": "まさに未踏の夢。だからこそ、知りたいのです。\nどうすれば、GⅠ7勝を超えられるのでしょうか？",
            "enText": "For many, a faraway dream. That's why we want \nto know. How can one surpass 7 G1 victories?",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 315,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 329,
                    "pathId": 1933992242848381179
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8627910997961619626,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "……そうですね。七冠は達成したものの、\nその先まで行けなかった私にはわかりようもありません。",
            "enText": "……that is the question, isn't it? Although I have achieved \n7 crowns, I was unable to break past that, so I'm at a loss.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 291,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 353,
                    "pathId": -4008617910756396692
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 272,
                    "pathId": -5837770466427411048
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1717736215684459869,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ですが――\nそれを果たしうるウマ娘ならば、自然と知っているのでしょう。",
            "enText": "However――When an Uma Musume that can achieve \nthat appears, I'm sure all eyes will be on her.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 205,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（……GⅠ7勝超え。とんでもない話だな）",
                    "enText": "(……7 G1 wins. That's quite the topic)",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（……GⅠ7勝超えか。とんでもない話）",
                    "enText": "(……7 G1 wins. That's quite the topic)",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 181,
                    "pathId": 3463472274971066921
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -6536012181067971961
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1584422822736069675,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そもそも、GⅠレースを1勝するだけでも凄まじい快挙。\nシンボリルドルフらのGⅠ7勝は、もはや神業のようなものだ。",
            "enText": "In the first place, winning just one G1 is an incredible \nachievement on its own. Symboli Rudolf and the others \nwith 7 G1 wins is already the longest of the long shots.",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（本当にいつか、現れるんだろうか）",
                    "enText": "(Will someone really be able to top that?)",
                    "nextBlock": 33
                },
                {
